Class LocalVacuumEnvironmentPercept

  • java.lang.Object
    • aima.core.agent.impl.ObjectWithDynamicAttributes

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Percept

    public class LocalVacuumEnvironmentPercept
extends DynamicPercept
    Represents a local percept in the vacuum environment (i.e. details the agent's location and the state of the square the agent is currently at).
    Author:
    Ravi Mohan, Ciaran O'Reilly, Mike Stampone, Andrew Brown
